==English==

===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} ''[[hungrig]]'', from [[hungor]] 'hunger' (from the same).

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈhʌŋ.ɡɹiː/}}
* {{audio|en-us-hungry.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj|hungri|er}}

# affected by [[hunger]]; desirous of food; having a physical need for food.
# {{figurative}} [[eager]], aving an avid [[desire]] ('appetite') for something.

